{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#6728: watch callback has something side effect when calling `createApp` in the callback",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:25:38.369695+00:00",
  "text": "watch callback has something side effect when calling `createApp` in the callback\n\n### Vue version\r\n\r\n3.2.39\r\n\r\n### Link to minimal reproduction\r\n\r\n[SFC Playground](https://sfc.vuejs.org/#)\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Open the [demo](https://sfc.vuejs.org/#)@vue3.2.39\r\n2. After clicking it, log `1,1,2,2` will appear\r\n\r\n![CleanShot 2022-09-23 at 18 01 40](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/18424466/191937534-f37fdbfb-d048-409f-90c9-1420b90eb25f.gif)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### What is expected?\r\n\r\n1. open the [demo](https://sfc.vuejs.org/#)@vue3.2.37\r\n2. After clicking it, log `1,2,1,2` will appear\r\n\r\n![CleanShot 2022-09-23 at 18 04 21](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/18424466/191937988-94ee75ea-09b0-4340-9c1b-ccc637afab99.gif)\r\n\r\n\r\n### What is actually happening?\r\n\r\nLog: 1, 1, 2, 2\r\n\r\n### System Info\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Any additional comments?\r\n\r\n_No response_",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    ":lady_beetle:  bug",
    "scope: reactivity",
    "has workaround"
  ],
